data.description: District 2, in the outskirts of Boiling Springs, you will find this beautiful home with 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms! Great location: right off of I-85, close to shopping, lake and hospital. This home has a great set up for entertaining with the Living Room, Kitchen and Dining all on one level. When you enter the foyer, go down the half stairs to a great entertainment space! All 4 bedrooms with a loft, or separate living room, are upstairs, with 2 full bathrooms. The bathrooms are spacious and beautifully redone - just look at the huge main suite and the gorgeous bathtub and separate shower! Like to enter through the side? Perfect! There is a huge Mudroom/ Laundry area with an extra storage space beyond the mudroom. No need to track in dirt and mud through the house. Fenced-in backyard with lots of space for entertaining outside. This home has so much to offer with such a great price and location!
